title: How to Breakthrough
itunes:title: How to Breakthrough
description:
Episode 184 - Some times we get the feeling that we have been stuck in the same place for a long time. We feel like there it something else that we should be doing but we can't figure out how to get there or what it is. What we need is a breakthrough and in this episode I talk about how to create a breakthrough.
